♪With blood burning, he's unrivaled♪

226
00:10:08,461 --> 00:10:13,645
♪Storming the heights,
who dares compete♪

227
00:10:14,848 --> 00:10:20,030
♪Sword in hand, he's unstoppable♪

228
00:10:21,056 --> 00:10:26,953
♪On the road to dreams,
he's fearless and dauntless♪

229
00:10:28,893 --> 00:10:32,925
♪Over vast earth, the hero sheds tears♪

230
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:39,348
♪Giving all out, he can never be swayed♪

231
00:10:41,807 --> 00:10:46,775
♪Heart consumed by fire, turning to ash♪

232
00:10:48,338 --> 00:10:52,000
♪Defying fate, he rises to immortality♪

